CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 19, 1956, pg. 7A, reads: "Planning for Fall - Mrs. William M. Cuthbert, left, chairman of East Area YWCA, and Mrs. Robert A. Moore, chairman of the St. Nicholas Fair, make plans for the event which is scheduled for Oct. 31 - Nov. 1, at the St. Nicholas Greek Orthodox Church, Dithridge St. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. William Cuthbert and Mrs. Robert Moore seated behind table with dolls, planning St. Nicholas Fair at St. Nicholas Greek Orthodox Church
